                  "revisionId": 2677686,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Primed Pressure Point is considered to be of the same type as the Pressure Point and Sacrificial Pressure , and none of these mods can be equipped together."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Primed Pressure Point",
                  "pageId": 1006498,
                  "revisionId": 2677686,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This mod has less damage increase per rank than its Common counterpart, making it less effective up to and including rank 7 because of higher capacity cost. For comparison, Pressure Point increases damage by 120% at rank 5, while Primed Pressure Point only increases damage by 90% at the same rank and cost."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Primed Pressure Point",
                  "pageId": 1006498,
                  "revisionId": 2677686,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Even at max rank, Primed Pressure Point is less effective compared to Pressure Point in Damage / Cost, but still remains more effective than Elemental mods, while also boosting them."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Primed Pressure Point",
                  "pageId": 1006498,
                  "revisionId": 2677686,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The difference in effectiveness is minimized, though not eliminated, if a Madurai-polarized slot is used, because Pressure Point's max rank (9) is an odd number, whereas Primed Pressure Point's max rank (14) is even."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Primed Pressure Point",
                  "pageId": 1006498,
                  "revisionId": 2677686,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "On a weapon modded with no other base damage-increasing mods (e.g. Spoiled Strike ), swapping out Pressure Point for Primed Pressure Point represents an increase of 2.65 ÷ 2.20 − 1 = 20.45% ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Primed Pressure Point",
                  "pageId": 1006498,
                  "revisionId": 2677686,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Primed Pistol Gambit , the only other Primed mod with a reduced effect per rank, also has reduced drain to balance out the lower gain, thus being more effective than its normal counterpart for any given mod cost."
                }
              }
